headline: Front-Month Gold Pushes to New Record High
summary: Front-month gold futures gained 0.4% to $2,947.90 a troy ounce, a new record. The volatility seen in politics domestically and abroad seems to be incentivizing some safe haven flows into gold — but not as much as expected, said Mizuho Securities USA.
